{
  "stem": "5559.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We said, [ROMANIAN]-- which means you can kiss my [ROMANIAN], you know where.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That we, yes-- and the professor heard it sometime.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we were not even-- they had fun.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They knew what it was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They called up the parents.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They called them to school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And you better watch your sons and your son, because you're going to be in trouble.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We don't go for that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They knew what it was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But I just want to bring out, they were very intelligent professors, you know, and very...",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And somehow because it was, I think-- although they wear the swastika just because they had to join.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Naturally, either you join or you get fired.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It was the [NON-ENGLISH], and such.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But they understood that these Jewish boys or whatever it was contribute, through all the thing, in the camaraderie among the kids in school, you know, was so close that they wouldn't try to punish.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Because they still want to keep the thing together.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "The Iron Guard was bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I want to repeat it, It was bad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "It was very sad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But it was still far off, whatever you heard, with-- out of-- with Hitler in Germany.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was sad.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "It were a lot of things, people were beaten up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Some were killed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But it was, by far, not that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I'm not defending the Iron Guard at all, because I had no sympathy whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I'm not saying that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I'm just saying it-- but I knew, but I learned later on that it was really a total different situation for students, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Because like you see, like I told you, a lot of the students they came to my home.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I taught him and everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "We were too close too friendly.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
